      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to be passing this beauty along to a new home. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014seriously, it still has that fresh new-car smell and hasn't seen a single scratch! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. You\u2019ve gotta come see it in person to believe how perfect it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
