    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is, without exaggeration, a showroom-preserved example that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous gloss with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings; it has been protected by a multi-stage ceramic coating and has lived its entire life in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains pristine, with the premium leather seating showing no signs of wear, bolsters that remain firm, and that distinct 'new car' scent still present. Every button, switch, and digital display functions perfectly, and the dashboard is free of any fading or heat damage. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been meticulously maintained with a full paper trail of scheduled services performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is spotless, the undercarriage is clean enough to eat off of, and the high-performance tires have nearly full tread remaining. This is a collector-grade vehicle for a buyer who demands the absolute best and refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
